# 09.04 Stage 2 — Agent Platform

## Overview

Stage 2 defines the transition of cmdOS from a single AI execution product into a scalable AI Agent platform.

The purpose of this stage is to enable developers, partners, and organizations to create, deploy, and distribute AI Agents inside the cmdOS ecosystem.

The focus moves from:

"One AI Agent performing tasks"

to:

"An ecosystem of AI Agents performing specialized tasks."

Core principle:

MVP

↓

Agent Framework

↓

Developer Ecosystem

↓

AI Agent Platform

---

# 1. Stage 2 Purpose

The purpose of Stage 2 is to build the foundation for an open AI Agent ecosystem.

The main objectives are:

- Create Agent development infrastructure
- Enable third-party Agent creation
- Build SDK ecosystem
- Introduce Plugin Marketplace
- Create reusable capabilities

