# 4. Agent Platform Architecture

The Agent Platform consists of several components.

---

# Agent Framework

## Purpose

Provide the foundation for creating AI Agents.

Capabilities:

- Agent creation
- Agent lifecycle management
- Task planning
- Memory management
- Communication

---

# Agent Runtime

## Purpose

Execute and manage Agents.

Responsibilities:

- Run Agents
- Monitor execution
- Manage resources
- Handle failures

---

# Capability System

## Purpose

Provide reusable actions for Agents.

Examples:

- API access
- Application control
- Data processing
- External services

---

# Plugin System

## Purpose

Allow external developers to extend cmdOS.

Includes:

- Plugin SDK
- Plugin validation
- Plugin marketplace

---

